# EWP-007 — WorkspaceMembership

**Engine:** VS08 – License, Subscription & Tenant Management Engine

**Milestone:** VS08A – Tenant Foundation

**Capability Contract:** CC-007 – WorkspaceMembership

**Status:** Approved for Implementation

---

# Objective

Implement the **WorkspaceMembership** aggregate exactly as defined by the approved CAP architecture.

WorkspaceMembership establishes operational access while preserving the separation between identity, organizational affiliation, and workspace participation.

---

# Inputs

Implementation shall comply with:

* ES-001 Database Standards
* ES-008 Architecture & Domain Modeling
* ES-009 Data Ownership & Persistence
* ES-010 Platform Naming & Namespace
* ADR-008-001 through ADR-008-017
* DDS-101A
* CC-007

---

# Scope

Implement only the WorkspaceMembership aggregate.

---

