* Remove Membership
* Update Workspace Role
* Get Membership by Id
* Get Membership by Workspace
* List Workspace Members

---

## Validation

Validate:

* Workspace exists.
* Workspace is Active.
* TenantMembership exists.
* TenantMembership is Active.
* Workspace and TenantMembership belong to the same Tenant.
* Membership uniqueness `(workspace_id, tenant_membership_id)`.
* Immutable associations.
* Valid lifecycle transitions.

---

